      "side": 1,
      "message": "I changed things slightly and I think it make more sense what is going on. This way I am still testing the public method and it allows for a fake cros_config command to be written alongside the test. I still have to change a package private (lowercase) variable but that seems to be acceptable in go tests, please correct me if I am wrong I am very new to go.",
